<li id="cite_note-39"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/spl/hi/uk/03/census_2001/html/ethnicity.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/shared/spl/hi/uk/03/census_2001/html/ethnicity.stm" rel="nofollow">BBC NEWS | CENSUS 2001</a></li>
